msgctxt "#32253"
msgid "Optional. If you have DarkSubs/All_Subs installed, you do not need Wyzie at all -- clicking any non-Hebrew subtitle in All_Subs will trigger AI translation automatically. Wyzie is only useful if you have NO other subtitle addon and want a one-click online source from inside this addon. 1000 requests/day on the free tier at store.wyzie.io/redeem."
msgstr "Optional. If you have DarkSubs/All_Subs installed, you do not need Wyzie at all -- clicking any non-Hebrew subtitle in All_Subs will trigger AI translation automatically. Wyzie is only useful if you have NO other subtitle addon and want a one-click online source from inside this addon. 1000 requests/day on the free tier at store.wyzie.io/redeem."

